text: Diogo Alberto Carvalho Torres (born 22 April 1987) is a Portuguese football player who plays for Merelinense. ==Club career== He made his professional debut in the Segunda Liga for Maia on 17 December 2005 in a game against Portimonense. ==References== ==External links== Category:1987 births Category:People from Maia, Portugal Category:Living people Category:Portuguese footballers Category:F.C.
